# PS-4: Decision Transparency
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: All major product decisions

ENFORCE: Every major decision must be documented with rationale and stakeholder input before execution.
PROHIBIT: Undocumented major decisions; proceeding without transparency confirmation.
ON VIOLATION: Escalate missing documentation to Product Governance Skill → halt execution.
